<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="floating-elements">
    <div class="floating-shape shape-1"></div>
    <div class="floating-shape shape-2"></div>
    <div class="floating-shape shape-3"></div>
    <div class="floating-shape shape-4"></div>
    <div class="floating-shape shape-5"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title">About Me</h2>
    <div class="header-accent"></div>
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-image">
        <div class="profile-ring">
          <div class="split-image">
            <img src="/profile-placeholder.jpg" alt="Profile Image" class="profile-img" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>
          Hello! To put simply, I like romanticising life.

        </p>
        <p>
            I enjoy learning about systems, deconstructing and understanding every aspect and component of them, to learn from and build better world models. I am a generalist learner; I do not believe people are so weak as to only need to 'specialise' in one thing. Perhaps to be world leading you must, but, is it really that impossible to be <b> great </b> at many things instead? I think not.
        </p>

                <p>
                    I've made full-stack web applications, data science projects and machine learning models (see projects).
        </p>
        <p>
            Interested in building things, designing systems, space, astronomy, neuroscience, and artificial intelligence. Also hiking and experiencing experiences.
        </p>

        <p>
            I am also extremely interested in agentic AI and the future of the world -- see <a href="https://github.com/astraedus" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">@astraedus</a> (<a href="https://astraedus.dev/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">astraedus.dev</a>) for some projects I've worked on.
        </p>
        <div class="skills">
          <h3>Skills</h3>
          <ul class="skills-list">
            <li>Machine Learning / Data Science</li>
            <li>Scalable and deployable systems</li>
            <li>JavaScript/TypeScript</li>
            <li>React.js</li>
            <li>Node.js</li>
            <li>HTML/CSS</li>
            <li>AWS</li>
            <li>Full Stack Development</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Technologies</h3>
          <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Python">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/python/python-original.svg" alt="Python">
              <span>Python</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Java">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/java/java-original.svg" alt="Java">
              <span>Java</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="C">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/c/c-original.svg" alt="C">
              <span>C</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="JavaScript">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/javascript/javascript-original.svg" alt="JavaScript">
              <span>JavaScript</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="TypeScript">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-original.svg" alt="TypeScript">
              <span>TypeScript</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="React">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/react/react-original.svg" alt="React">
              <span>React</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Node.js">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/nodejs/nodejs-original.svg" alt="Node.js">
              <span>Node.js</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Expo">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/expo/expo-original.svg" alt="Expo">
              <span>Expo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Supabase">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/supabase/supabase-original.svg" alt="Supabase">
              <span>Supabase</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Tailwind CSS">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@latest/icons/tailwindcss/tailwindcss-original.svg" alt="Tailwind CSS">
              <span>Tailwind</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Bash">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/bash/bash-original.svg" alt="Bash">
              <span>Bash</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="AWS">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/amazonwebservices/amazonwebservices-original-wordmark.svg" alt="AWS">
              <span>AWS</span>
              <div class="tech-hover-detail">
                Lambda, DynamoDB, EC2, S3
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Git">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/git/git-original.svg" alt="Git">
              <span>Git</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Linux">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/linux/linux-original.svg" alt="Linux">
              <span>Linux</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Docker">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-original.svg" alt="Docker">
              <span>Docker</span>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item" data-tech="Machine Learning">
              <img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/tensorflow/tensorflow-original.svg" alt="Machine Learning">
              <span>ML/AI</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-alt);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ---- Floating Elements ---- */
  .floating-elements {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .floating-shape {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.07;
    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    filter: blur(1px);
  }

  .shape-1 {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    top: 15%;
    left: 10%;
    animation-delay: 0s;
  }

  .shape-2 {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-color), var(--primary-color));
    top: 25%;
    right: 15%;
    animation-delay: 1s;
    animation-duration: 8s;
  }

  .shape-3 {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(225deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--accent-color));
    bottom: 20%;
    left: 5%;
    animation-delay: 2s;
    animation-duration: 7s;
  }

  .shape-4 {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    background: linear-gradient(315deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
    top: 60%;
    right: 25%;
    animation-delay: 3s;
    animation-duration: 9s;
  }

  .shape-5 {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--secondary-color), var(--primary-color));
    bottom: 35%;
    right: 10%;
    animation-delay: 4s;
    animation-duration: 5s;
  }

  /* ---- Container ---- */
  .container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .header-accent {
    width: 60px;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  /* ---- Content Layout ---- */
  .about-content {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ---- Profile Image ---- */
  .about-image {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: flex-start;
    position: relative;
  }

  .profile-ring {
    position: relative;
    padding: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
    animation: profileFloat 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.15), 0 0 60px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.05);
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .profile-ring {
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.12), 0 0 60px rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.04);
  }

  .split-image {
    position: relative;
    width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .split-image:hover {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }

  .profile-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* ---- About Text ---- */
  .about-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* ---- Skills ---- */
  .skills h3 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .skills-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .skills-list li {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.15);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .skills-list li {
    background: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.15);
  }

  .skills-list li:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
    background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--glow-primary);
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .skills-list li:hover {
    background: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.15);
  }

  /* ---- Tech Grid ---- */
  .tech-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(80px, 1fr));
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tech-item {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.85rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--glass-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .tech-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--card-hover-shadow);
    border-color: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.2);
    background: rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.05);
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .tech-item:hover {
    border-color: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.2);
    background: rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.05);
  }

  .tech-item img {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, filter 0.3s ease;
    filter: brightness(0.9);
  }

  .tech-item:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.1);
    filter: brightness(1.1) drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(100, 255, 218, 0.3));
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .tech-item:hover img {
    filter: brightness(1.1) drop-shadow(0 0 6px rgba(8, 145, 178, 0.2));
  }

  .tech-item span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-text-alt);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .tech-item:hover span {
    color: var(--primary-color);
  }

  .tech-hover-detail {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2.5rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    white-space: nowrap;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
    border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .tech-item:hover .tech-hover-detail {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* ---- Animations ---- */
  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg);
    }
    33% {
      transform: translateY(-15px) rotate(120deg);
    }
    66% {
      transform: translateY(10px) rotate(240deg);
    }
  }

  @keyframes profileFloat {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0px);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
    }
  }

  /* ---- Responsive ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-image {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .split-image {
      width: 200px;
      height: 200px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
